Legacy
======

Legacy is a science fiction themed simulation game in which the player controls
a colony on an isolated planet in the far reaches of the galaxy.  The goal is to
build the colony, explore the planet, and generally survive and even thrive.

The source for the game is in the subdirectory 'legacy'.

Instructions on how to build and install the project can be found in the file
'INSTALL'.

Conditions of copying or distributing this game and its source can be found in
the file 'COPYING'.

Current releases are designed to buil tested in the build directory:  the search
paths and installation paths for assets have not been properly establinshed.
'sokay, cos the current version soesn;t do much but put up a splash screen
anyways.

Have fun.

